Library of Loudwater

Overview

Located in Loudwater

Goods and Services

Services Sold: Information

Story

Rowena used to work for this library. She studied other worldly tomes. The library itself was magical. It was built by Rowena’s grandparents. On entering the library most people do not realize that the building could not possibly hold what all is inside. Unless the person frequently goes to the library (like someone that works there or studies there) when they leave they don’t fully remember it all. Their minds rationalize the size to be different than what it actually is.
